node.text:
Landscape of Shadows. CDG FW21 from today at CDG Aoyama
 
Amidst the incessant overflowing of miscellaneous things, the deluge of colour, the flooding of sound and the inundation of information….
 
…..I needed to take one breath in the monochrome stillness
